data.description: Welcome home to this single level 3-bedroom 2 bath home w/ carolina room and 2 car garage. This home features a in-ground pool with NO HOA and a beautiful lake view!  Recent improved to this home include new kitchen cabinets, new counter tops, new tile backsplash, new hardware/fixtures throughout, stainless steel appliances, new water heater, new luxury vinyl plank flooring and fresh paint throughout. The large living room area features vaulted ceilings with ceiling fan. A Carolina Room just off the living room features leads out to the fenced back yard featuring an in-ground pool and large storage shed!   The master bedroom features a tray ceiling and walk in closet.  The master bath has been improved with a new vanity, new countertop and new framed mirror. Both guest bedrooms feature ceiling fans and good-sized closets.  This home is in the desirable Castlewood community and is just a short distance from area schools, dining, entertainment venues and area beaches! This one will not last long.  Call today to schedule your showing!
